name: Boxed In and Drowning
description:
The weight of the world on your back. Inequality, discrimination, violence, and wars. All to make one feel superior over another. The rich get richer, the poorer get poorer. People are divided based on race, class, sexuality, religion, sex and politics, it’s ‘us vs them’.

We are all human. That is the bottom line, remove our clothes, our skin, we are all the same pile of flesh and bones, it’s time we start acting like it.

by Dehiscence 2021, 5400px X 7200 px
